5140" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" styl=
e=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width:=
 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-=
color: #ccc;">$7.7 billion of those securities</a> demanded their money bac=
k, which cost Barclays hundreds of millions more dollars. It does not seem =
to have disclosed an exact number, but in July it <a href=3D"https://link.m=
ail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29264112.275527/aHR0cHM6Ly9ob21lLmJhcmNsYXl=
zL2NvbnRlbnQvZGFtL2hvbWUtYmFyY2xheXMvZG9jdW1lbnRzL2ludmVzdG9yLXJlbGF0aW9ucy=
